high_descs: Turn left and walk to the CD's to the right of the statue on the dresser.
Pick up the CD closest to the back wall.
Walk to the front of the dresser.
Place the CD in the third drawer down on the right.
Walk to the CD to the left of the statue on the dresser.
Pick up the CD to the left of the statue.
Walk to the front of the dresser.
Place the CD to the right of the other CD in the third drawer down on the right.
anns.task_desc: Place two CD's in the third drawer down on the right side of the dresser.

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the end of the white dresser.
Pick up the closest disc off of the white dresser.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the front of the dresser.
Open the drawer that is second from the bottom on the right side of the dresser and place the disc inside in the back left corner.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the dresser.
Pick up the disc that is closest to the digital alarm clock on the dresser.
Turn around and walk towards the bed, then turn around again to and walk back up to the dresser.
Open the second drawer from the bottom on the right side of the dresser and place the disc inside to the right of the disc that is already in there, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two discs into a drawer.

high_descs: Move to the dresser ahead of the fire place
Pick up a CD from the dresser
Move to the front of the dresser
Put the CD inside and close the drawer
Move to the left side of the dresser ahead of the fire place
Pick up a CD from the dresser
Move to the front of the dresser
Put the CD inside and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put two cds inside a drawer of the dresser ahead of the fire place.

high_descs: move forwards a bit, then turn around and face the right side of the dresser cabinet
grab a CD off of the cabinet there
turn left and walk past the dresser a bit, then turn right and walk forwards to face the center of the dresser on the right
place the CD inside of the third drawer from the top on the right side
move to the left a bit and face the dresser again
grab a CD off of the top of the dresser
move to the right a bit and back up enough to put space between you and the dresser
place the CD inside of the third drawer from the top on the right side
anns.task_desc: place two CD's in the dresser drawer

high_descs: Turn directly around to the dresser behind you.
Grab the CD that is right in front of you.
With the CD in hand turn and go to the front of the dresser.
Place the CD in the third drawer down on the right side of the dresser.  Place it on the back left side of the drawer.
Turn and go to the other side of the dresser so you are facing the alarm clock.
Pick up the CD that is to the left of the statue.
Turn around and go to the right side of the dresser with the CD in hand.
Open the third from the top on the right side drawer.  Place the CD in the drawer to the right of the other CD that is in there.
Turn around to face the white dresser.
Pick up the CD closest to you on the dresser.
Turn left, walk forward, turn to face the white dresser.
Open the third drawer on the right side of the dresser and put the CD inside. Close the drawer.
Turn to the left then turn to face the white dresser.
Pick up the CD on the dresser beside the black cell phone.
Turn around and face the dresser, open the third drawer on the right side of the dresser.
Place the CD in the drawer to the right of the other CD. Close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two CDs into the third drawer on the right side of the white dresser.
